data.description: *CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS*  This stunning 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom home with a bonus room offers luxury and comfort in the prestigious golf community of the country club. With over 3,700 sqft of living space, this all-brick home boasts high-end features including a screened in-ground saltwater pool, and a spacious covered patio for entertaining in your privacy fenced yard. Highlights include a new roof installed in January 2019 and a new pool pump installed in 2019. Inside, you'll find 12-foot ceilings, crown molding, and impeccable craftsmanship throughout. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream with custom cabinetry, 5-burner stove,  beautiful range hood, stainless steel appliances, a double oven, an island with a prep sink, a walk-in pantry, and a generous breakfast bar. The master suite is a retreat with private access to the back patio, a luxurious master bathroom featuring columns, a tiled shower, a double vanity, and a jacuzzi tub. As you enter this home, you'll be captivated by the quality craftsmanship, from the accent beams at the entryway to the updated flooring. Additional features include a formal dining room, a breakfast nook, custom fixtures, and a decorative fireplace. Each of the other 3 bedrooms has its own private bathroom, ensuring comfort and privacy for all. Upstairs, a bonus room with a full bath offers versatility as an additional bedroom, movie room, or exercise space. The oversized garage provides ample space for vehicles and a golf cart, allowing you to fully enjoy the amenities of this remarkable community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your dream home.
